## ğŸ’¡ Command Line Usage

```bash
# Start new experiment
mltrackflow init --name my_experiment

# List experiments
mltrackflow list

# Generate report
mltrackflow report --experiment iris_demo

# Compare models
mltrackflow compare --experiment iris_demo --runs rf svm logistic
```

